sentences: Jacob Mark "Jake" Pitts (born August 21, 1985) is an American musician and record producer best known as the lead guitarist of rock band Black Veil Brides.
Pitts received his first guitar when he was 10 years old, but he put it away and did not play it for a few years.
Pitts received his first guitar when he was 10 years old, but he put it away and did not play it for a few years.
He is a certified recording engineer and went to Los Angeles Recording School in 2006.
He is also producing for other bands such as New Years Day.
On January 18, 2014, his mother, Carolyn, died.
Pitts married Cory Logvin Pitts on February 3, 2017.
